df_ = df_images[(df_images['partition'] == 2)].sample(TEST_SAMPLES)

x_ = []
y_ = []

for index, target in df_.iterrows():
    if "'" in index:
        index = index[1:]
        index = index[:-1]
    im = cv2.imread(images_folder + index)
    im = cv2.resize(cv2.cvtColor(im, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB), (218, 178)).astype(np.float32) / 255.0
    #im = np.expand_dims(im, axis =0)
    x_.append(im)
    #y_.append(target['Attractive'])
    z =  np_utils.to_categorical(target['Eyeglasses'],2)
    y_.append(z)
    
x_test = np.array(x_)
y_test = np.array(y_)
